title: Test
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Yes, and No.
The line for Yes has the highest values across Year with a mean value of 52.33,
and it peaked at 18-34_years with a value of 60.0.
No mostly had the least y-axis name with a mean value of 47.67,
which peaked at 65+_years with a value of 53.0.
Overall No is gradually increasing, Yes is gradually decreasing,  throughout the Year
The difference of y_axis name between Yes and No is smaller at Year Total compared to the Year 18-34_years.
The greatest difference of y_axis name between Yes and No occurs at Year 18-34_years and the smallest difference occurs at 35-44_years.
